{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-index-js","path":"/blog/2017-02-08-windows-process-command","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"author":"Young Hwang","date":"2021-04-13","title":"Windows Process Command","path":"/blog/2017-02-08-windows-process-command"},"html":"<h2>특정 포트 오픈 확인</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">netstat -na | findstr [Port]\n</code></pre>\n<h2>열려 있는 포트 PID 확인</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">netstat -nao | findstr [Port]\n</code></pre>\n<h2>PID 찾기</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">tasklist | findstr [PID Number]\n</code></pre>\n<h2>프로세스 죽이기</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">taskkill /f /pid [PID Number]\n</code></pre>"}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}